      "content": "hey, i’ve been having these really intense flashes lately. like, when i meditate, i don't just see images, i feel like i’m accessing actual data or memories that aren't mine, like they're coded into my dna or something. it feels way more real than just a dream. do u know any specific ways to focus on that to actually unlock what's in there?",
